metadata.name: Lion King (1/1) Digital + Physical
metadata.description:
The Lion King NFT collection is a one-of-a-kind set of digital assets that are stored on the ETH blockchain. When you purchase an NFT from this collection, you will receive a physical oil on canvas artwork with dimensions of 68.5 x 60 cm, created by the talented artist Predrag PeÄ‘a Radovanovic. This artwork is a true masterpiece, and owning an NFT from this collection is a unique opportunity to own a piece of digital art history. 
Questions? Please contact: info@radovanovic.art
